description:
Bimi Boo with you again! This time you will visit Bimi Boo friends who live in a treehouse. You will meet a sly cat, funny rabbit and cute squirrel. There is an exciting game in the house of your baby in which he can help to arrange things in the right way, put them in the order and feed Bimi Boo friends.

30 different games will fascinate your child with not only bright colors and funny animations, but also with interesting and clear tasks such as:

- Arrange items by color, shape, number and size;
- Pick up items within the meaning of;
- Arrange the geometric shapes according to the silhouette;
- Sort items in its place
- Feed animals in the right way;
- Restore pictures from memory.

Together with Bimi Boo Shapes & Colors, your baby will learn how to distinguish things by its shape, color, texture and quantity. The game also improves fine motor skills, attention and intelligence. It contains everything you need for a fun and healthy development of the child.
